it remembers\.\.
db2(testdb) => list tables for schema xyz
db2(testdb) => select * from xyz\.tab[double\-tab]
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0

.
.TP
\fBYou can pipe\fR
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf


